    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/a858a8928e39e46939fe7bda5bddf6e0.poster.avif?t=1755529131\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/a858a8928e39e46939fe7bda5bddf6e0.webm?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/a858a8928e39e46939fe7bda5bddf6e0.mp4?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 现代风格的动作类开放世界射击游戏 — 单兵突击或与好友组队协同作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从安全区搭乘突击直升机直接空降到战场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 经过简化的生存机制，适合更重视采取行动，而不大喜欢精细管理的玩家</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/48e7908ccb54cc5f48b919c61e316d26.poster.avif?t=1755529131\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/48e7908ccb54cc5f48b919c61e316d26.webm?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/48e7908ccb54cc5f48b919c61e316d26.mp4?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 针对第 4 季而推出的全新基地建设系统 – 收集资源、建设、突袭、防御和摧毁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集资源并寻找武器、弹药和补给 — 制作物品，如无人机</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 64 平方公里的大幅定制地图 – 针对第 4 季而推出的新地图 – 达到原来世界面积的 4 倍</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9e2947cbda07c377a879664daf54109a.poster.avif?t=1755529131\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9e2947cbda07c377a879664daf54109a.webm?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9e2947cbda07c377a879664daf54109a.mp4?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 针对第 4 季而推出的全部新任务系统 – 战役奖励 - 5 个难度等级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 即将推出每日任务，以及有意义的玩家奖励</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 常规的游戏内事件：核反应器、组合攻击、无线电塔、民用堡垒、坠毁的直升机 — 风险越高，奖励越丰厚</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9080648beae75581b82cae422bb0a84e.poster.avif?t=1755529131\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9080648beae75581b82cae422bb0a84e.webm?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/9080648beae75581b82cae422bb0a84e.mp4?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 全新的角色定制 — 体型、面容、皮肤、头发、眉毛、眼睛和全套服装系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集武器皮肤和其他自定义物品，进行交易 — 用普通物品兑换稀有物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam 市场支持 – 买卖皮肤 – 完成您的收集！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 争夺每个赛季中各个类别的榜单排名</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/b5d1a6efb55d45c15c3c35b2b99dea7b.poster.avif?t=1755529131\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/b5d1a6efb55d45c15c3c35b2b99dea7b.webm?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625340/extras/b5d1a6efb55d45c15c3c35b2b99dea7b.mp4?t=1755529131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过我们的 Discord 频道直接联系开发团队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 致力于为我们的玩家带来公平的商业模式 – 不存在货币化惩罚</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>人工智能时代已经来临。一台原型战斗机器人在遭到法律封禁并等待 XERA 公司进行安全销毁的时候产生了自我意识。它逃了出去并开始以工业化规模进行复制，从此让世界陷入了混乱。一旦远程关闭人工智能的尝试失败，就注定会引发一场人类无法承受的战争。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>一个又一个的国家为了争夺资源控制权，抵御机器人而卷入了战争。在世界其他地方军事力量的关注下，无权无势的人们聚集起来，洗劫了 XERA的残余设施，建立了两个前沿作战基地，而森林四周的安全区则成为了人类丧失领导权之后的藏身之地。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> 基地之间的交战根本没有规则可言。唯一重要的就是活下来。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XERA: Survival 由 Spotted Kiwi Interactive 开发，这是一家位于新西兰南岛 (Aotearoa) 的独立开发公司，其团队成员遍布世界各地：4位来自新西兰，1位来自智利，1 位来自俄罗斯，还有1位来自美国 。</p>",
